productReviews.reviewText: I tried to electrocute it but got sweetmeat all over it.
My neighbor Georgine has one of these. She works as a fireman and she says it looks colorful.
My Shih-Tzu loves to play with it.
The box this comes in is 3 inch by 6 centimeter and weights 15 ounce!
i use it barely when i'm in my store.
